description:
This is a 13 minute workout called '10 Min Fat Burning Workout | No Equipment' from the channel THENX.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow along with Chris Heria as he shows you 10 Min Fat Burning Workout with No Equipment. This workout will have you burning calories and give you real results by increasing your endurance and muscle definition.
